        <item>
          <title>New England hires former Patriots Super Bowl champ Mike Vrabel as coach</title>
          <description><![CDATA[The New England Patriots have hired Mike Vrabel as their head coach. The team announced the hiring Sunday morning, a week after Patriots owner Robert Kraft fired Jerod Mayo following the team’s season-ending victory over the Buffalo Bills. Mayo finished 4-13 in his lone season.]]></description>
